pageProduct.name: Ostelin Bone Strength + Collagen Support 120 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
Information

Why Bone Strength matters

Reaching peak bone mass

Strong bones are essential for quality of life, as bones provide the structure for our bodies*. Peak bone mass is reached in our 20s**, but no matter your age, it will make a difference to make decisions that support long-term bone strength. Consuming enough vitamin D and calcium is one way to achieve this.

*Better Health Channel. Bones. 2012

**Mitchell PJ et al. Life-course approach to nutrition. Osteoporos Int. 2015, 26(12), 2723 2742

Bone Strength Collagen Support

Collagen is the most abundant structural protein in the body and is found in bones. Ostelin Bone Strength Collagen Support provides key nutrients to maintain bone strength, plus Vitamin C to support collagen production. Vitamin D3 helps increase calcium absorption, and it maintains muscle function and healthy immune system function.

Dosage for Adults: Take 2 tablets daily with a meal or as directed by your healthcare professional.

Ostelin Bone Strength Collagen Support Product Benefits

Contains vitamin C, which supports collagen production.

Contains calcium and vitamin D3 to maintain bone strength.

Maintains muscle function and healthy immune system function.

No added gluten, lactose, dairy products, artificial flavours or sweeteners.

General Information

Maintain bone strength.
Supports collagen production.

• Ostelin Bone Strength + Collagen Support provides key nutrients to maintain bone strength plus vitamin C to support collagen production.
• Vitamin D3 helps increase calcium absorption. It maintains muscle function and healthy immune system function.
• Calcium supports bone strength.

Size: 120 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• Contains calcium and vitamin D3: To maintain bone strength
• Contains vitamin C: To support collagen production
• Other product benefits: Maintains muscle function and healthy immune system function
• Dosage: Take 2 tablets daily with a meal or as directed by your healthcare professional
• This medicine may not be right for you. Read the warnings before purchase, in warnings section below. Follow the directions for use.

Warnings

Contains soya and sulfur dioxide.

Ingredients

Colecalciferol (Vitamin D3 500IU) 12.5micrograms
Calcium ascorbate dihydrate (Vitamin C 25mg) 30.26mg
Calcium (from Calcium carbonate) 150mg
Hydrolysed Collagen 325mg
Copper (from Cupric sulfate) 1mg
Manganese (from Manganese sulfate monohydrate) 2.5mg

Contains: NO ADDED: Gluten, lactose, artificial flavours, artificial sweeteners, or dairy products.

Contains Soya and sulfur dioxide.

Directions

For adults: take 2 tablets daily with a meal or as directed by your healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.
Protect from moisture.
